<!DOCTYPE html>
<!-- saved from url=(0051)file:///C:/Users/bavya/bakers-bridge/get-badge.html -->
<html><head><meta http-equiv="Content-Type" content="text/html; charset=windows-1252">
    <title>Get Your Elite Badge</title>
    <style>
        body { font-family: sans-serif; display: flex; flex-direction: column; align-items: center; justify-content: center; height: 100vh; background: #FAF7F2; margin: 0; }
        .card { background: white; padding: 40px; border-radius: 30px; shadow: 0 20px 40px rgba(0,0,0,0.1); text-align: center; border: 1px solid #C5A059; }
        img { width: 300px; height: 300px; margin-bottom: 30px; border-radius: 50%; box-shadow: 0 10px 30px rgba(197,160,89,0.3); }
        h1 { color: #2D2926; margin-bottom: 10px; }
        p { color: #8D6E63; margin-bottom: 30px; font-size: 14px; }
        .btn { background: #C5A059; color: white; padding: 15px 30px; border-radius: 50px; text-decoration: none; font-weight: bold; text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: 1px; transition: all 0.3s; display: inline-block; }
        .btn:hover { background: #2D2926; transform: scale(1.05); }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="card">
        <h1>Your Elite Badge is Ready!</h1>
        <p>Right-click the image below and select <b>"Save Image As..."</b><br>Save it as <b>elite-badge.png</b> in this folder.</p>
        <img src="./elite-badge_files/elite_badge_design_1777625097184.png" alt="Elite Badge">
        <br>
        <div class="btn">Right-Click Image to Save</div>
    </div>


</body></html>